metadata.name: Baba Yaga
metadata.description:
Baba Yaga is a witch that explore the world to bring more souls to her master, the Devil King. Extremely know in the Russian folklore to scary bad children. It's said that she eat them to keep her youth, creepy isn't ? 

I decided to do an original design for her. Some hands (children dead body?) recover her body, a really mysterious woman. Just an advice, she can do very powerful spell, so maybe you are already bewitched by her ? 

To thanks every bidders, a stamp will be send ! For the great winner, a PFP and an unique NSFW art will be give. I think you understand, you can't miss Baba Yaga !
